<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pre-Placement Self Assessment Program</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .text-img-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .text-img-container .text {
            flex-basis: 60%;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .text-img-container .image {
            flex-basis: 35%;
        }

        .text-img-container img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        @@media(max-width: 768px) {
            .text-img-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .text-img-container .text,
            .text-img-container .image {
                flex-basis: 100%;
                margin-right: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Pre-Placement Self Assessment Program</h1>
        <p><b>"Start your journey towards success today and unlock your full potential with our dynamic self-assessment program. Your future begins here!"</b></p>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Welcome to the Self Assessment Program</h2>
            <p>This Program is a prominent online platform dedicated to aiding job seekers, students, and career enthusiasts with a vast repository of resources and education and skill development, this platform will serve as a versatile hub for individuals preparing for competitive exams, job interviews, and placement assessments</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-img-container">
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Assessment Interface</h2>
                    <p>Upon submitting your answers, our platform provides immediate feedback, allowing you to track your progress and understand your strengths and areas for improvement. Each question is accompanied by detailed explanations, enabling you to grasp concepts effectively and enhance your understanding.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="~/svg/localhost_44357_Assessment_Index_ExamId=7850&Questionid=0 (1).png" alt="Assessment Interface Screenshot">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-img-container">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="~/svg/localhost_44357_Dashboard_Index (2).png" alt="Dashboard Screenshot">
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Dashboard Overview</h2>
                    <p>
                        Embark on your journey towards success with  Google Bar Chart section, allowing you to visualize your progress and identify areas for improvement. Track your performance effortlessly with features like Exam History, Exam Status, ensuring you're always aware of where you stand. Plus, with Exam Summary,
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more sections for additional screenshots -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-img-container">
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Exam History</h2>
                    <p>Here, you'll find a detailed record of all your completed exams, empowering you to track your progress. Resume your unfinished assessments with ease, picking up right where you left off in your quest for improvement. Need a fresh start? Simply delete past exams and start anew, ensuring you stay focused on your current goals.</p>
                    <p><b>"Your exam history is not just a record of the past; it's a roadmap to your future success. Dive in, explore, and let your journey towards greatness continue!"</b></p>
                </div>
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="~/svg/localhost_44357_ExamHistory_Index.png" alt="Feature X Screenshot">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-img-container">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="~/svg/localhost_44357_ExamManager_Index.png" alt="Feature Y Screenshot">
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Build Exam</h2>
                    <p>Here, you have the power to tailor your assessment experience to suit your unique preferences and learning style. Customize your exam with <i>Custom Exam, Simulated Exam, Quick Exam</i></p>
                    <p><b>Craft Your Path to Success</b></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
